WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000 line:90%
I invented a
new kind of 
crutch 
so I could 
carry my son.

00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:06.500 line:90%
It can be used
as a normal
crutch

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:12.500 line:90%
But when
needed I switch
to hands-free
mode.

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:18.500 line:90%
Again:
normal crutch...

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:24.500 line:90%
...or hands-free
crutch!

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:29.000 line:90%
It's useful to
carry glasses

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:32.500 line:90%
plates,

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:36.000 line:90%
or teapots!

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:44.000 line:90%
I no longer need
help at the
canteen!

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:53.000 line:90%
And I can carry
armfuls, like
everyone who 
swore they didn't
need a basket ;)

00:00:54.500 --> 00:01:05.000 line:90%
I can even carry
heavy stuff...

00:01:06.500 --> 00:01:11.500 line:90%
...or heavier stuff!

00:01:13.500 --> 00:01:18.500 line:90%
It's also
compatible with
smartphone
addiction :)

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.000 line:90%
And last detail:
it doesn't fall when
put against a wall :)

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:30.500 line:90%
Next, I want to turn
this prototype into
a product to help
others like me

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:37.500 line:90%
...so stay tuned!




